        <div n="807-001D" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-1"> Wou'd you rise in the Church be stupid and dull:<ref target="#spp-807-001D-footnote-1">1</ref><note place="foot" n="1" xml:id="spp-807-001D-footnote-1">Ardmagh</note></l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-2"> Be empty of Learning of Insolence full;<ref target="#spp-807-001D-footnote-2">2</ref><note place="foot" n="2" xml:id="spp-807-001D-footnote-2">Dublin</note></l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-3"> Tho' lewd and immoral, be formal and grave,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-4"> In flat'ring an Artist, in fauning a Slave;<ref target="#spp-807-001D-footnote-3">3</ref><note place="foot" n="3" xml:id="spp-807-001D-footnote-3">Killala</note></l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-5"> No merit no Science no virtue is wanting,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-6"> In him that's accomplish'd in cringing &amp; canting.</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-7"> Be studious to practise true meaness of Spirit</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-8"> For who but Lord <hi rend="black-letter">Bolton</hi> was miter'd for merit,</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-9"> Wou'd you wish to be wrap'd in a Rochet──in short,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-807-001D-line-10"> Be poxd and profane as Fanatical Hort.<ref target="#spp-807-001D-footnote-4">4</ref><note place="foot" n="4" xml:id="spp-807-001D-footnote-4">Killmore</note>807-001D   </l></lg></div>
